text.div: Selected laboratory tests for Male,Female, Native Hawaiian or Other Pacific Islander,Asian,Unknown,American Indian or Alaska Native,Other patients aged 20-24 seen as either outpatients or inpatients at Johns Hopkins Hospital, JHCP, and Bayview between 3/1/2016 and 3/1/2018 having a diagnosis of asthma recorded on the problem list or as an encounter diagnosis.
